      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;d-none d-md-block&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;persona position-relative row mt-5 align-middle p-3&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;div class=&#34;col-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;                &lt;div class=&#34;position-absolute top-50 start-0 translate-middle-y col-4 ps-3&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;img-fluid rounded-5&#34;&#xA;        src=&#34;https://metaphysx.com/images/bio-photo-2800x2800.png&#34;&#xA;        &#xA;        &#xA;        srcset=&#34;https://metaphysx.com/images/bio-photo-576x576.webp 576w, https://metaphysx.com/images/bio-photo-768x768.webp 768w, https://metaphysx.com/images/bio-photo-992x992.webp 992w, https://metaphysx.com/images/bio-photo-1200x1200.webp 1200w, https://metaphysx.com/images/bio-photo-1400x1400.webp 1400w, https://metaphysx.com/images/bio-photo-2800x2800.webp 2800w&#34; sizes=&#34;100vw&#34;&#xA;        height=&#34;2800&#34;&#xA;        width=&#34;2800&#34;&#xA;        alt=&#34;metaphysx&#34;&gt;&#xA;                &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;            &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;            &lt;div class=&#34;col-10 bg-secondary text-bg-secondary rounded-5 fs-md-5 fs-6 pe-5 pb-3&#34;&gt;&#xA;                &lt;div class=&#34;row&#34;&gt;&#xA;                    &lt;div class=&#34;col-3&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;                    &lt;div class=&#34;col-9&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;fs-3 mt-4&#34;&gt;metaphysx&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;“This is the way that I think about my life, and I hope that you&amp;rsquo;ll think of your life too.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You should think about your life hoping that there will be many moments in it about which you can say; There is no place I&amp;rsquo;d rather be, there is no thing I&amp;rsquo;d rather be doing, there is nobody I&amp;rsquo;d rather be with, and this I will remember well.”&lt;/p&gt;</description>
